main event: Two round bluish objects, the size of a basketball, were observed rising out of trees and performing circular flight before disappearing.
interesting points: The objects were visible for about 8 to 10 minutes before fading out of sight., The sighting lasted approximately forty minutes in total., The direction of observation was towards the northeast., There was a possibility that the objects were balloons or misidentified shooting stars., Another observer was reported to have a simultaneous sighting, though no details are known.
